SUMMARY:BayCare Presents: Proton Therapy: A New Era in Cancer Treatment
LOCATION:Tampa \, FL United States
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an easy-to-understand overview of proton therapyan
  advanced form of radiation that uses the power of physics to target tumor
 s with remarkable precision while protecting healthy tissue. Well break do
 wn how it works\, who may benefit\, and why it can offer fewer side effect
 s by minimizing damage to healthy organs. This straightforward session exp
 lains the science in simple terms and highlights when and why proton thera
 py is becoming an increasingly important option in modern cancer care. Apr
 il 22\, 2026 12-12:45 pm Register Here (https:events.teams.microsoft.comev
